{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act33side", "eventName": "巴別塔", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BB-ST-1", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "未完成的告別", "storyInfo": "特蕾西婭遇刺，女妖也為“魔王”唱響輓歌，凱爾希在特蕾西婭彌留之際趕回了她的身邊，目睹了一切早已結束的現場。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_5_7_shining", "fadetime": 0.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormlp", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 3.0, "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男孩在夢中哭泣，女孩將男孩裹在自己抵擋風雪的斗篷中，為他拭去了眼淚。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冰冷。斷續。呼嘯。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨人輕輕講述一部遙遠的史詩……"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的聲音穿越了風雪的裂隙。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眾魂的呼喚為其和音，男孩的嗚咽敲打著節拍。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女孩在夢中的酷寒中微微喘息，她捂住了男孩的眼睛，然後閉上了眼。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "千年前的歌謠仍在他們眼前演繹。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "我見遠方的軍隊襲來家園，", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "text": "從河谷到山崗，從高山到平原。", "x": 300.0, "y": 410.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st4", "text": "君王授首，眾魂慟哭。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st4"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st5", "text": "我見六位英雄跨過魔王屍骸，", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st6", "text": "吹響號角，率萬部回擊。", "x": 300.0, "y": 410.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st5"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st6"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st7", "text": "可惜，可嘆，烈怒火光洶湧澎湃，", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st8", "text": "流浪者的城市滅於一旦。", "x": 300.0, "y": 410.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st7", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st8", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "我見黑色的冠冕浮現，", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "榮耀、恩典與救濟悉數歸於雙子。", "x": 300.0, "y": 410.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "text": "裂隙擴散，新誕的一切盡數背叛。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st4", "text": "我見風暴降臨，風暴中央的，", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st5", "text": "乃是弑君之刀劍，誅王之槍矛，", "x": 300.0, "y": 410.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st6", "text": "終結傳說皆是按照公義。", "x": 300.0, "y": 450.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st4", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st5", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st6", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“這就是此章的結尾。”"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨人淡入了夢中的風雪中，將孩子拋棄在身後。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男孩漸漸不再聽到自己啼哭的聲音。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他醒了。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_thundercloud", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0, "x": 0.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 20.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.1, "yScaleTo": 1.1, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "1094年夏"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾地區，荒廢小鎮外"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是此章的結尾，阿斯卡綸。我的故事說完了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我的族人……獨眼巨人深入北境前，最後望向卡茲戴爾的所見。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一章是已然逝去的未知歷史，是尚未臨近的可能未來，抑或是毫無意義的囈語？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "近千年來，無人知曉……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到他們出現，命運的湍流開始岔進更窄、更確定的河道……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，她所見的命運，已經近在眼前。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_laccolith", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不關心。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1294_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "right"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳，難得你有耐心聽我說完。", "name": "“疤眼”"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅色的鮮血慢慢沿著他的面具下沿滑落到了他的胸口。"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯卡綸微微眯眼，他已走投無路。"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會死，所以我給你最後的尊重。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "right"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳。呵。", "name": "“疤眼”"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從我們認識開始，你從未把那些個預言放在心上，對吧？", "name": "“疤眼”"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "right"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……你永遠不會理解一個貪婪的人對控制命運的渴望。", "name": "“疤眼”"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死前少廢話。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "right"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你急著去和巴別塔那些人會合，但現在還沒到你走的時候。你看，天災快到了。", "name": "“疤眼”"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……我倒開始好奇了。", "name": "“疤眼”"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在風暴之中，找到了什麼？", "name": "“疤眼”"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓開。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "right"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "委託必須完成，這是我自己在疤痕商場定下的規矩。", "name": "“疤眼”"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論生——", "name": "“疤眼”"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 0.3, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.31}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cnstrctnck"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "shake", "power": 10.0, "times": 50.0, "duration": 0.4}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "right"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃！", "name": "“疤眼”"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.15, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯卡綸的身形在他的背後消失，同一時間，薄暮般的霧氣已經繞緊巨人的脖頸，將他的身軀高懸於危崖之外。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你有看到過自己的結局嗎？", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1294_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我不在乎預言，和你一樣，哈。", "name": "“疤眼”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1294_1#2$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但事實就是，我們都逃不開命運。你不想掙扎嗎？憑什麼？為什麼？怎麼能夠？", "name": "“疤眼”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1294_1#2$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要忘了，預言中也有你的一席之地——", "name": "“疤眼”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1294_1#2$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚咽。風暴。"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哀婉的吟唱在他們的耳畔響起，來自女妖河谷的輓歌掠過地平，捲入風暴中央。"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯卡綸的身體不由自主地戰慄著，她渾身冰涼。"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一陣無法訴說的刺痛從她的耳後一路激盪到腳底。"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有名字的輓歌，不祥的預兆。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#7$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1294_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別了……卡茲戴爾。", "name": "“疤眼”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1294_1#2$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯卡綸聽到了一聲嘆息。"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cnstrctnck"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的手越握越緊，直到“疤眼”的喉嚨無法發出一絲輕微的聲音。"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，她鬆開了手。"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哈，該死的命運。", "name": "“疤眼”"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眨眼間，獨眼巨人的巨大身體成了懸崖下一個渺小的點。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薄霧在狂風中散去，連同兜帽投下的陰影一起，消失在墜落懸崖的淚水中。"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喘息聲，天災雲中低沉的雷鳴，風沙席捲荒地的呼嘯……"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬物的聲音歸於沉寂。"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_victoria", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞，倫蒂尼姆"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼……", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屬於她的薩卡茲，抬起頭。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你們還要履行她交予的使命，我就站在這裡，等你們上前。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我准許你們為她復仇。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "刺殺者"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 1.0, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的衣服上，繡了我的名字。", "name": "刺殺者"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是特蕾西婭殿下親自刺繡的，而它此刻正微微發燙，我知道……這意味著什麼。", "name": "刺殺者"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭殿下交給我們的任務已經結束了。", "name": "刺殺者"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不再向你舉劍。薩卡茲不會在外敵前刀劍相向。", "name": "刺殺者"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我們，向你效忠，攝政王。", "name": "刺殺者"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你仍然抱有對薩卡茲的熱忱，我們便甘願把性命交給你。", "name": "刺殺者"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使你們險些毀掉了我們在維多利亞的一切布置？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果軍事委員會決定讓我們死，我們可以死。", "name": "刺殺者"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要這能帶來更好的結果……", "name": "刺殺者"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那便如她所願。", "name": "刺殺者"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們方才還是險些葬送計劃的叛黨頭目，讓我怎麼相信——", "name": "曼弗雷德"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曼弗雷德。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“如她所願”，是嗎。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#3$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的名字，劊子手。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤莉葉。", "name": "刺殺者"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會記住你的名字，也會交給你最後的任務。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "衛兵，刺客，傭兵，這場血戰的每一位倖存者——我要你們踏入諸王長眠之所。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要你們拆碎維多利亞的鋼鐵心臟，在那裡伏擊並剿滅所有的蒸汽騎士。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是軍事委員會削弱倫蒂尼姆的核心計劃，讓我們也參與？", "name": "尤莉葉"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曼弗雷德會看好你們。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是不是，不可能活著離開那裡？", "name": "尤莉葉"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大可去爭取。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "尤莉葉"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……還有什麼事嗎？", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是看看，是什麼樣的人培養出了阿斯卡綸。", "name": "尤莉葉"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她始終沒有擺脫你。", "name": "尤莉葉"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#3$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1299_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……在我發誓追隨特蕾西婭殿下時，從未想過那一對改寫了卡茲戴爾歷史的混血雙子的故事會如此落幕。", "name": "尤莉葉"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更沒想到，原來我這種賤命胚子，也在這段故事之中有了一席之地。", "name": "尤莉葉"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "永別了，特雷西斯殿下。", "name": "尤莉葉"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會把對你的憎恨，帶進墳墓。", "name": "尤莉葉"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_corridor_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾地區，巴別塔羅德島本艦"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_doorclose"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$act18d0d0_intro", "key": "$act18d0d0_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1307_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "300,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1", "posfrom": "-300,0", "posto": "-100,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“凱爾希，繼續走。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自誕生於世的那一天起，凱爾希從未感到這道長廊如此漫長。"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#6$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mon3tr！", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#6$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "npc_10002"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$char_Mon3tr"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（憤怒的嘶吼）", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "npc_10002"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1307_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "power": 15.0, "times": 50.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-70", "duration": 0.5, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，咳哈。", "name": "無名的刺客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1307_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勛爵……", "name": "無名的刺客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1307_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要安葬我們，卡茲戴爾的土地再不能容下更多叛徒了。", "name": "無名的刺客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1307_1#1$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "了結他。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#6$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "npc_10002"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$p_skill_Mon3trburst"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我知道，即使孤身一人，你的腳步也不會停下。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭！博士！", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#4$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$Mon3tr_n"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "npc_10002"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（焦急的嘶鳴）", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "npc_10002"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#4$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$alarmenter"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "系統無回應……這……", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mon3tr，切開門！", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#6$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "npc_10002"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$char_Mon3tr"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（狂暴的嘶吼）", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "npc_10002"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 40.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_doorclose"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.21}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mon3tr，熔毀！", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#7$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 50.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$char_Mon3tr"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“你相信孤獨獨屬於你，你相信自己沒有同類。但是，自你再度甦醒的那一天起，我們便並肩而行，不是嗎？”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不朽的帝國化為齏粉，神民的權杖在先民的呐喊中被折為兩段，天幕上浪湧般的脈衝，群星自璀璨閃耀到暗淡解體的不變規律……"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "消亡，新生，萬物輪迴，於她從不陌生。"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "npc_10002"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$Mon3tr_n"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（興奮的嘶吼）", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "npc_10002"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.3}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "-100,0", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.3}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 40.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_explosion_stone"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#4$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭——", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#4$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#10$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“……可總有一天，我會選擇放慢腳步，停留在某處。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“那時候，請不要悲傷，凱爾希，繼續走。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希下意識地搜索腦海中的記憶……"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "消亡，新生，萬物輪迴。"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一次，不一樣。不太一樣。"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她第一次，必須與第一位能與她平等交流的摯友告別。"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "49_i01", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 60.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭……", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“所以，凱爾希，到了該告別的時候了。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭……博士……", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這……", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我總是說，我們的流浪終有一天會結束，薩卡茲的流浪終有一天會結束……”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“你的流浪……也已走到了終點……”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明知道這樣的可能性始終存在……為什麼……", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我應該留下，是我……", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“因為我相信羅德島，相信巴別塔……相信你。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“凱爾希，我希望這艘船，羅德島，能成為你的家。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我已經做了我能做的。我不會抱怨自己的結局。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“巴別塔的使命結束了，你們和這艘船卻才剛剛起程。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我不是你的同類，凱爾希。我沒法解開你的疑惑。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“但我一直是你的同伴。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“從前，現在，未來……”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我會一直陪伴著你們。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“那麼……”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}